==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Shack up
<hw>Shack" up`</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>to live together
in a sexual relationship, without being legally married.</def>
<mark>[Slang, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>to live in a cabin, shack, or other crude
dwelling.</def> <mark>[Slang, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Shad</ent>⟦br⟧
